<br>
Regular exercise is the key to losing weight. Best thing is to &quot;force&quot; yourself to exercise. For example, if you gonna study at university, try to live at some student house 10-20 min away from your lecture hall, in that way you will be forced to walk/run everyday maybe even more than once per day! If you are overweight, you would reach normal weight in no-time, even if you eat unhealthy food. <br>
<br>
Regular exercise &gt; unhealthy food<br>
<br>
Believe me, I have tried it myself, eating junk food alot but running/walking 5 times per week, and I have seen it on others. To try change what you eat in order to lose weight, I do not believe that. I believe in exercise for sure. I gained weight after 1 year of EQing, but I always take longer breaks (2-3 months) and can easily catch up with my fitness again. That is no problem for me. <br>
<br>
<br>
Its when you sit down and play EQ for 7 hours per day (which you can do if you are in AV, LoV, Aurore, Reviction, Triune, FE, TW, ZH) that is dangerous... especially if you do not exercise.. cuz you will feel the need to raid everyday to get more uber and to get more keys for cod, tt, pot etc.<br>
<br>
So sooner or later I think everyone of us will need a little break, to realize we need some physical exercise <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> )) <br>
<br>
Personally I am having a EQ break now myself, gonna do lots of studies and physical exercise during this time. prolly a month or 2, spend some time with my gf and enjoy RL a lil. I think everyone needs that from time to time.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm3.showMessageRange?topicID=789.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm3.showMessageRange?topicID=789.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm3.showMessageRange?topicID=789.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm3.showMessageRange?topicID=789.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a> <b>5</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm3.showPrevMessage?topicID=789.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm3.showNextMessage?topicID=789.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=789.topic&index=99><img src=http://www.pwshift.com/tr/images/mt/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm3.emailToFriend?topicID=789.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm3.threadControl?topicID=789.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/posticons/techops.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm3.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=789.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm3.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=789.topic>Unsubs